title: RNFA Orange County, CA (46743822) at Soliant Health (California)
text: Source: Soliant Health Operating Room RN First Assistant Orange County, CA Live and work in the posh scenery of Orange County! RNFA certification must be through an accredited organization 8 hour flexible shift M-F ACLS PALS preferred Experienced a variety of specialties, such as Ortho and General cases, like laparoscopic Experience with robotic cases If interested in this position, please contact Allison Lewis at 770-325-0558 or allison.lewis@soliant.com.
